{# templates/manager/en_attente.html.twig #}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Demande en attente — Manager MABB</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #063a55 0%, #0b4fa3 60%, #1c88b6 100%);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            padding: 30px 16px;
        }
        .card-wait {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px 36px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 520px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon-wait {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #fc702a;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50% { opacity: .65; transform: scale(.95); }
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0b1f3a;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: .92rem;
            margin-bottom: 26px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .demande-card {
            background: #fff7ed;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .demande-club {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .demande-role {
            font-size: .82rem;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .demande-date {
            font-size: .72rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .badge-status {
            background: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: .68rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            letter-spacing: .5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }
        .btn-action {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: .9rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0;
            color: #475569;
            background: #fff;
            transition: all .15s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .btn-action:hover {
            border-color: #1c88b6;
            color: #0b4fa3;
            background: #f0f9ff;
        }
        .btn-logout {
            border-color: #fecaca;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .btn-logout:hover {
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #dc2626;
            border-color: #dc2626;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #1d4ed8;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            font-size: .82rem;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card-wait">
        <div class="icon-wait">⏳</div>
        <h1>Demande en attente de validation</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            Bonjour {{ app.user.prenom }} ! Ton inscription au club est bien enregistrée,
            mais un dirigeant doit valider ta demande avant que tu puisses accéder au Manager.
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle"></i>
            <strong>Pourquoi cette étape ?</strong>
            Pour préserver la qualité des échanges au sein du club, chaque adhésion est
            validée par un dirigeant. Tu seras notifié dès que ta demande sera approuvée.
        </div>

        {% for d in demandes %}
            <div class="demande-card">
                <div class="demande-club">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i> {{ d.club.nom }}
                </div>
                <div class="demande-role">
                    Rôle demandé : <strong>{{ d.roleDemande ?: d.role }}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="demande-date">
                    Demandé le {{ d.createdAt|date('d/m/Y \\à H:i') }}
                </div>
                <span class="badge-status">
                    <i class="bi bi-hourglass-split"></i> EN ATTENTE
                </span>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="https://mabb.fr" class="btn-action">
                <i class="bi bi-house"></i> Retour au site MABB
            </a>
            <a href="{{ path('manager_logout') }}" class="btn-action btn-logout">
                <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right"></i> Se déconnecter
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
